                                "start": 0,
                                "stop": 9.45,
                                "byte_start": 92289,
                                "byte_stop": 130114,
                                "text": "The judgment and opinion of the Court in No. 8 Original, State of Arizona against the State of California will be announced by Mr. Justice White."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 9.45,
                        "stop": 227.655,
                        "byte_start": 130114,
                        "byte_stop": 1002918,
                        "speaker": {
                            "ID": 15071,
                            "name": "Byron R. White",
                            "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/people\/byron_r_white",
                            "last_name": "White",
                            "roles": [
                                {
                                    "id": 2715,
                                    "type": "scotus_justice",
                                    "date_start": -243367200,
                                    "date_end": 741243600,
                                    "appointing_president": "John F. Kennedy",
                                    "role_title": "Associate Justice of the Supreme Court of the United States",
                                    "institution_name": "Supreme Court of the United States",
                                    "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/preson_role\/scotus_justice\/2715"
                                }
                            ],
                            "thumbnail": {
                                "id": 32699,
                                "mime": "image\/png",
                                "size": 55559,
                                "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/sites\/default\/files\/byron_r_white.png"
                            },
                            "length_of_service": 11396,
                            "identifier": "byron_r_white"
                        },
                        "text_blocks": [
                            {
                                "start": 9.45,
                                "stop": 31.875,
                                "byte_start": 130114,
                                "byte_stop": 219871,
                                "text": "This -- this case began way back in 1952 when Arizona filed a motion for -- leave to file as a case against California to settle the respective shares of the Lower Basin States in the Colorado River."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 31.875,
                                "stop": 39.008,
                                "byte_start": 219871,
                                "byte_stop": 248397,
                                "text": "We appointed a Special Master who took evidence for several years and filed a massive report."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 39.008,
                                "stop": 49.493,
                                "byte_start": 248397,
                                "byte_stop": 290297,
                                "text": "The case was argued twice and finally opinion was announced in 1963 and a decree entered in 1964."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 49.493,
                                "stop": 62.496,
                                "byte_start": 290297,
                                "byte_stop": 342333,
                                "text": "That decree settled the amount of water that the Upper Basin States were to deliver to the Lower and also settled the shares of the Lower Basin States among themselves."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 62.496,
                                "stop": 73.265,
                                "byte_start": 342333,
                                "byte_stop": 385383,
                                "text": "The decree also determined the water rights of the Indian reservations in the Lower -- in the Lower Basin."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 73.265,
                                "stop": 87.135,
                                "byte_start": 385383,
                                "byte_stop": 440867,
                                "text": "The -- we retained jurisdiction, however, for various reasons among others because the so-called presently perfected rights that would have priority had not yet been determine."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 87.135,
                                "stop": 99.065,
                                "byte_start": 440867,
                                "byte_stop": 488619,
                                "text": "Also, there were boundary disputes about the Indian reservations that still have to be finally determined."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 99.065,
                                "stop": 108.028,
                                "byte_start": 488619,
                                "byte_stop": 524459,
                                "text": "In 1979, we amended the decree when they -- when the presently -- present perfected rights have been determined."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 108.028,
                                "stop": 119.52,
                                "byte_start": 524459,
                                "byte_stop": 570434,
                                "text": "But meanwhile, the Indian tribes and later the United States moved to reopen the proceedings in two respects."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 119.52,
                                "stop": 143.152,
                                "byte_start": 570434,
                                "byte_stop": 664998,
                                "text": "First, it was alleged that in the proceedings leading up to the 1964 decree, the -- a fair amount of irrigable acreage had been mistakenly overlooked and that the -- then additional water rights were -- should be allocated to the reservations."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 143.152,
                                "stop": 158.696,
                                "byte_start": 664998,
                                "byte_stop": 727169,
                                "text": "Secondly, it was said that the boundary disputes had been finally determined and that the -- the -- there was a good deal additional territory to be included in the Indian reservations and hence more water to be allocated."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 158.696,
                                "stop": 173.742,
                                "byte_start": 727169,
                                "byte_stop": 787355,
                                "text": "We appointed a Special Master who took a testimony and took up -- who heard the case and he recommended that in almost all respects the -- that we accept the claims of the tribes in the -- in the United States."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 173.742,
                                "stop": 178.942,
                                "byte_start": 787355,
                                "byte_stop": 808149,
                                "text": "Exceptions were filed and briefed and -- and argued."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 178.942,
                                "stop": 187.197,
                                "byte_start": 808149,
                                "byte_stop": 841167,
                                "text": "And now for the reasons stated in an opinion on file with the clerk, we sustain the exceptions of the -- of the States."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 187.197,
                                "stop": 197.842,
                                "byte_start": 841167,
                                "byte_stop": 883695,
                                "text": "We hold that the irrigable acreage issue was fully litigated and finally determined in the 1964 decree and was not subject to relitigation."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 197.842,
                                "stop": 213.73,
                                "byte_start": 883695,
                                "byte_stop": 947225,
                                "text": "Secondly, with some minor exception or two, we hold that because litigation is still pending with respect to the boundary disputes those boundaries have not yet been finally determined."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 213.73,
                                "stop": 216.549,
                                "byte_start": 947225,
                                "byte_stop": 958509,
                                "text": "Accordingly, we sustain the exception of the States."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 216.549,
                                "stop": 222.16,
                                "byte_start": 958509,
                                "byte_stop": 980975,
                                "text": "Justice Brennan joined by Justices Blackmun and Stevens has filed a dissenting opinion."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 222.16,
                                "stop": 227.655,
                                "byte_start": 980975,
                                "byte_stop": 1002918,
                                "text": "Justice Marshall took no part in the determination or consideration of the case."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
